Responsive Design?: Responsive Design is the practice of creating websites that provide a good user experience on any device without requiring separate desktop and mobile versions.

Instead of creating:
- Desktop website
-Tablet website
-Mobile website
-> You create one website that adjusts its layout based on the available screen size

Enduku Responsive Design Important? - Imagine you're building an e-commerce site

